DATA SOURCES & ATTRIBUTION

All financial data in this repository is sourced from public documents
published by the Government of India:

  • CAG Annual Finance Accounts (2023-24) — Comptroller & Auditor General of India
    https://cag.gov.in/

  • State GSDP — Ministry of Statistics & Programme Implementation (MoSPI / CSO)
    https://mospi.gov.in/

  • Geographic boundaries — Administrative boundary data for India
    (Simplified and projected from publicly available GeoJSON)

This project does not claim ownership of any government data. All fiscal and
geographic data remains the property of the respective Government of India
ministries and bodies. It is reproduced here under fair use for public
research, education, and policy analysis.

